Package: sobol
Type: Package
Title: Sobol Sequence Generator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Angel", "Robles", email = "alrobles@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides a fast and efficient implementation of Sobol sequence
    generation for quasi-Monte Carlo methods. Includes both batch and incremental
    interfaces with support for arbitrary starting indices and reproducible sequences.
